## Step 6: Plug in the known values to calculate $E_i$.
$E_i = 4.478 \, \mathrm{eV} + 13.598 \, \mathrm{eV} - 2.651 \, \mathrm{eV}$

## Step 7: Perform the arithmetic to find $E_i$.
